description:
A country official receives certain gifts from other countries on his visit. Different countries have different policies for these gifts. It is actually state-owned property but in Pakistan, the policy for these gifts is that an official can take this gift by paying a certain percentage of money otherwise it will be auctioned.

The Data Released by Cabinet Division of Pakistan.
The political affiliation was also added and the cost of gifts is in PKR/=.
title: Gift Received by Pak Officials 2002-22 Tosha Khana
